Package: magnemite
Type: Package
Title: Magnetogram Curation and Clustering Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Joey", "Frost-Xenopoulos",
      email = "joeyfrostxenopoulos@trentu.ca",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Workflows for historical magnetogram processing,
  manual curation, and time-series preparation. Provides reproducible path
  helpers, web asset and index generation, Shiny apps for clipping and timing
  tick correction, and reusable preprocessing and functional clustering
  utilities migrated from legacy analysis notebooks.
